## Sort chart values

1.  Click the 3 line menu to open the chart definition
<img src="../assets/chart_sort_1.png"  style="width:700px" class="border"></img>

<img src="../assets/chart_sort_2.png"  style="width:700px" class="border"></img>

2.  Click the sort by field and select the desired sort order

